The 26th is the day before Philippine President Duterte delivered his fifth State of the Union address (SONA) during his term of office. On the same day, the Philippines has confirmed more than 80,000 cases of COVID-19, among which the number of confirmed cases by the staff of the Presidential Department of Information (PCOO) and its directly affiliated institutions has increased to 25.
