Yinchuan: Classified policies to support kindergartens to stabilize the teaching team-Xinhuanet
Xinhua News Agency, Yinchuan, July 26 (Reporter Ai Fumei) Affected by the epidemic, kindergartens in Yinchuan City, Ningxia have not yet resumed, especially private kindergartens have increased financial pressure, which has a certain impact on the stability of kindergarten teachers and the sustainable development in the future.
In view of this, Yinchuan City has taken a number of measures such as pre-allocation of subsidy funds for inclusive private kindergartens, stabilizing post subsidies for non-inclusive private kindergartens, and reducing rent for private kindergartens to support these kindergartens to stabilize the teaching team.
According to the relevant policies of Yinchuan City, during the epidemic, if the organizers of inclusive private kindergartens (including the kindergartens that have been converted into inclusive kindergartens after the governance of supporting kindergartens in urban communities) refer to the minimum wage standards of the three districts and pay the basic living expenses of not less than 1,660 yuan per month to the faculty and staff of the basic living expenses of not less than 1,660 yuan per year, the municipal finance will pre-allocate 6 months of subsidy funds to solve the teachers' salaries and social insurance expenses according to the average cost of inclusive private kindergartens per student per year.
For non-inclusive private kindergartens that also pay basic living expenses of not less than 1,660 yuan per person per month, Yinchuan City will arrange 6 months of subsidy funds for preschool teachers according to the standard of 500 yuan per student per year.
At the same time, for private kindergartens renting state-owned assets for business use, Yinchuan City will reduce the rent of houses for three months during the period of epidemic prevention and control, and encourage developers and other rental entities to assume social responsibility, reduce the rent of kindergartens. If the rent is reduced for more than three months, the relevant tax and fee will be reduced according to the policy regulations.
