The receiving unit of the army will scientifically formulate plans for enlistment and professional training, and conscientiously organize training; After the completion of the training, in accordance with the principle of professional corresponding and consistent recruitment, the recruited non-commissioned officers will be uniformly and accurately assigned to the corresponding professional and technical posts.
